Ashley Madekwe https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ashley_Madekwe 0 Ashley Madekwe (born 6 December 1983) is a Nigerian English actress. She is known for her roles as call girl Bambi in the ITV2 series Secret Diary of a Call Girl, social climber Ashley Davenport on the ABC drama series Revenge and the witch Tituba in the WGN America series Salem.
